{"tid":2233653,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我個friend就嚟比棵蔥累死","createTime":"2020-10-07T09:38:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T18:02:28.000Z","uid":262455,"like":6,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"404035b6de059964045aea60ca2590a50e7241e7","tid":2233653,"uid":262455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T09:38:14.000Z","msg":"我個friend 自從一年前識左兩棵蔥之後<br />\n所有活動跟齊<br />\n而家仲每月進貢，正苦成皮野有大半拎左去買蔥<br />\n早幾日兩棵蔥出左周邊，成本價幾蚊雞扣心口既章賣成$100一個<br />\n我fd二話不說即刻訂左4個(圖案一樣只係背景色唔同)<br />\n據我所知佢已經冇咩錢，我叫佢翻下工<br />\n但係佢話要長期oncall睇有冇新蔥<br />\n而家同佢出街基本上佢都係望手機📱<br />\n我懷疑佢已經入緊魔<br />\n<br />\nSor for 1999，明就明"},{"pid":"5a5e24c75b55a99e45caad6ff5206423718efcb7","tid":2233653,"uid":153781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T09:41:01.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你個friend係咪成日去夾公仔"},{"pid":"8d404935ee0a62108760c70d788fdc84c385f4bb","tid":2233653,"uid":54502,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T09:50:07.000Z","msg":"正苦成皮野人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n二級工人都唔止啦"},{"pid":"b4e1a09379bfe6314a7e9337b9ac9914175a7a41","tid":2233653,"uid":87917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8d404935ee0a62108760c70d788fdc84c385f4bb","tid":2233653,"uid":54502,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T09:50:07.000Z","msg":"正苦成皮野人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n二級工人都唔止啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T09:51:47.000Z","msg":"是咪講緊之前派個一皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b9f1f4dfc45f0f3abec8cc005e9383b25a2e5fb","tid":2233653,"uid":262455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a5e24c75b55a99e45caad6ff5206423718efcb7","tid":2233653,"uid":153781,"like":1,"disli